<h2 class="section-heading">Why Sports Matter at MHSK</h2>
<p>Beyond the trophies, sports build something deeper: a sense of community and belonging. When students participate in teams and clubs, they connect to the institution, feel valued, and develop camaraderie that lasts a lifetime. Most importantly, sports give every student a chance to develop their leadership skills  captains, vice-captains, and team representatives learn responsibility long before the boardroom.</p>

